the most generic type of item: an action performed by a direct agent and indirect participants upon a direct object
the most generic kind of creative work, including books, movies, photographs, software programs, etc.
an article, such as a news article or piece of investigative report. Newspapers and magazines have articles of many different types and this is intended to cover them all
a work of art that is primarily visual in character
an event happening at a certain time and location, such as a concert, lecture, or festival

a publication event corresponds indifferently to the event of publication for a Creative Work of any type e.g. a broadcast event, an on-demand event, a book/journal publication via a variety of delivery media.
a utility class that serves as the umbrella for a number of 'intangible' things such as equivalent class
an organization such as a school, NGO, corporation, club, etc.
being that has certain capacities or attributes constituting personhood (avoid use with "instance of"; use "human" for human beings)
common name of Homo sapiens, unique extant species of the genus Homo
entity, something: human being, person, humankind, people, homosapien

the most generic type of item: entities that have a somewhat fixed, physical extension.
Any offered product or service. For example: a pair of shoes; a concert ticket; the rental of a car; a haircut; or an episode of a TV show streamed online.
